{"tid":194234,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇畫板推薦","createTime":"2017-04-09T23:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T12:12:21.000Z","uid":59624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"defcf4f776550c69e97dc5f5d77c3333429fdab7","tid":194234,"uid":59624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:13:24.000Z","msg":"我原本想買wacom ctl 490<br />\n筆直最多都預600左右<br />\n490個價錢都最啱<br />\n其實對入門呢講係咪好夠架啦?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2f6116b015512d523284553b018d4c07b994e1","tid":194234,"uid":59624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:18:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4094b7e7da1bf0fba50b20cd3231acbb3d097612","tid":194234,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我原本想買wacom ctl 490<br />\n筆直最多都預600左右<br />\n490個價錢都最啱<br />\n其實對入門呢講係咪好夠架啦?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買671，個人覺得中板size好用啲<br />\n不過你執相定畫畫？"},{"pid":"5640d1aa83aefa81dda5d7b74708ec84ebb85cd5","tid":194234,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:41:05.000Z","msg":"同意樓上，中板最好用"},{"pid":"0518b605e90e80947a89a9d62f514d91b43d73b6","tid":194234,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T23:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意樓上，中板最好用</blockquote><br />\n細板買完一定後悔，而且671size細又輕，唔同以前啲中板<br />\n舊3代啲中板同依家啲大板一樣大，依家啲中板同3代細板差唔多size仲要薄左<br />\n不過671最唔好就係支筆唔好渣"},{"pid":"b8b3240d95ce42c86ec272878100ff258b57f813","tid":194234,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同意樓上，中板最好用</blockquote><br />\n細板買完一定後悔，而且671size細又輕，唔同以前啲中板<br />\n舊3代啲中板同依家啲大板一樣大，依家啲中板同3代細板差唔多size仲要薄左<br />\n不過671最唔好就係支筆唔好渣</blockquote><br />\n而家大板都係唔好用，太大塊隻手要郁嘅範圍太大好易攰<br />\n<br />\n用緊intuos pro medium"},{"pid":"92ec9a8cffd2a92ef71b83ce0efe70d38b593bff","tid":194234,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同意樓上，中板最好用</blockquote><br />\n細板買完一定後悔，而且671size細又輕，唔同以前啲中板<br />\n舊3代啲中板同依家啲大板一樣大，依家啲中板同3代細板差唔多size仲要薄左<br />\n不過671最唔好就係支筆唔好渣</blockquote><br />\n而家大板都係唔好用，太大塊隻手要郁嘅範圍太大好易攰<br />\n<br />\n用緊intuos pro medium</blockquote><br />\n係唔係做3d同畫野其實買大板有啲多餘<br />\n中板出job方便<br />\n我用慣3代依家轉671一樣筆壓但價錢平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c48f8f2b399b10bbcd910eb74e5cb8531862aa","tid":194234,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:20:55.000Z","msg":"大家係用有線定無線嘅畫板?<br />\n<br />\n我硬係覺得好似無線好啲咁, 但係無線又要叉電, 其實邊樣好啲?"},{"pid":"1067e32812e24a0b82f75d7e4ec2e7d27129f551","tid":194234,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家係用有線定無線嘅畫板?<br />\n<br />\n我硬係覺得好似無線好啲咁, 但係無線又要叉電, 其實邊樣好啲?</blockquote><br />\n其實睇需要，個人覺得無咩大分別<br />\nBtw我習慣用無線板坐係張床對住個32吋mon執相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a584c2b9a964203f5758b58d866699246717b3f1","tid":194234,"uid":59624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:08:39.000Z","msg":"其實我係想買呢畫畫多d"},{"pid":"2da757fec252acc08706c49517f03dd36d17f3e8","tid":194234,"uid":59624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"我想問下樓上講既671係咪叫bambooone medium<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a306779ce3d33d26b7e8dba2f0741ca78e473b35","t