s=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n671只可以用呢款筆"},{"pid":"7f55f4d7f5c38783c2a79f980beae2e54c2fb575","tid":194234,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家係用有線定無線嘅畫板?<br />\n<br />\n我硬係覺得好似無線好啲咁, 但係無線又要叉電, 其實邊樣好啲?</blockquote><br />\n其實睇需要，個人覺得無咩大分別<br />\nBtw我習慣用無線板坐係張床對住個32吋mon執相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你用邊隻model既無綫線畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ed96e16e2ae3d6867e691acda66ade58020d2a","tid":194234,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家係用有線定無線嘅畫板?<br />\n<br />\n我硬係覺得好似無線好啲咁, 但係無線又要叉電, 其實邊樣好啲?</blockquote><br />\n其實睇需要，個人覺得無咩大分別<br />\nBtw我習慣用無線板坐係張床對住個32吋mon執相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你用邊隻model既無綫線畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢塊，好平<br />\n但成日要差電好煩<br />\n連支筆都要差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無電真係企撚左係度<br />\n<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.1.25crSF&amp;id=37263046765&amp;cm_id=140105335569ed55e27b&amp;abbucket=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.1.25crSF%26id%3D37263046765%26cm_id%3D140105335569ed55e27b%26abbucket%3D12&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f30a78f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.1.25crSF&amp;id=37263046765&amp;cm_id=140105335569ed55e27b&amp;abbucket=12</a>"},{"pid":"30d40cd8b0312edce2873dab67c8cd8874902623","tid":194234,"uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我原本想買wacom ctl 490<br />\n筆直最多都預600左右<br />\n490